data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 10.3-acre expanse with agricultural zoning sits this 2042 SF home. This unique property is a blend of comfort, space, and pastoral charm, featuring a spacious main residence, a versatile game room with an attached living unit, and a functional shed, all set in serene natural surroundings. The main home welcomes you with its inviting and open living space, comprising 2 well appointed bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the ground floor. The charm extends to the upper level where an open loft bedroom with its own bathroom offers a private and serene retreat. As you step inside, your eyes are immediately drawn to the brick fireplace in the family room, making it the perfect space to cozy up on those cold evenings. The heart of the home is the fully-equipped kitchen featuring SS appliances, bright, white cabinets and a breakfast bar which opens to a welcoming dining area, ideal for family meals and gatherings. Sliders off the living room lead to a screened in porch allowing you to enjoy the peace and quiet this property offers. Outside at the front of the house, the game room, perfect for entertainment and leisure, is complemented by an adjacent, comfortable 1BD/1BA unit, offering versatility and privacy for guests or the teen of the home. The outdoor living experience is enhanced by the vast 10.3 acres of picturesque land, presenting numerous opportunities for agricultural activities, outdoor recreation, or simply enjoying the tranquility of nature. Cool off during those hot days in the above ground pool. A practical shed on the property adds utility, ideal for storage or workshop needs. This property's location combines the peace of countryside living with the convenience of being within easy reach of local shopping and dining. Ideal for those seeking a tranquil lifestyle, this property offers spacious living, limitless possibilities for personalization, and the charm of rural life. It's a rare find for anyone looking to enjoy the benefits of ample land, versatile living spaces, and the tranquility of a natural setting. Updates in the last 3 years include a new septic and well. Enjoy!
